{"tid":2159399,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"留下，因為這是我的家","createTime":"2020-08-16T09:58:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T17:59:45.000Z","uid":231886,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ed83ee382d0fe3969adc208462d59fc8deec7205","tid":2159399,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:58:29.000Z","msg":"專訪】當國安法掀起移民潮 居港日籍插畫家：留下，因為這是我的家<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tEbtK8u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtEbtK8u.png&h=e6d370af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA-%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E6%8E%80%E8%B5%B7%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E6%BD%AE-%E5%B1%85%E6%B8%AF%E6%97%A5%E7%B1%8D%E6%8F%92%E7%95%AB%E5%AE%B6-%E7%95%99%E4%B8%8B%E5%9B%A0%E7%82%BA%E9%80%99%E6%98%AF%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%B6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%258E%2580%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%25BD%25AE-%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%25B1%258D%25E6%258F%2592%25E7%2595%25AB%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E7%2595%2599%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%259B%25A0%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%2580%2599%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25AE%25B6%2F&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJKof2S8NuZTczTYEA3Eyx%2FE%3D&h=7d11eb93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%258E%2580%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%25BD%25AE-%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%25B1%258D%25E6%258F%2592%25E7%2595%25AB%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E7%2595%2599%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%259B%25A0%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%2580%2599%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25AE%25B6%2F&h=be69758e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA-%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E6%8E%80%E8%B5%B7%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E6%BD%AE-%E5%B1%85%E6%B8%AF%E6%97%A5%E7%B1%8D%E6%8F%92%E7%95%AB%E5%AE%B6-%E7%95%99%E4%B8%8B%E5%9B%A0%E7%82%BA%E9%80%99%E6%98%AF%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%B6/</a><br />\n<br />\n來港七年，日籍插畫家奈緒子（Mango Naoko）帶著一套畫具，一本素描簿，到訪香港每一片角落，以畫筆記錄城市點滴。<br />\n<br />\n自言喜愛著這個地方的她，卻從不以「香港人」自居，「我一直在中間，以前日本『屋企』的生活態度我已經不習慣，可是香港的也有很多不習慣，但以前到現在，我每天都在了解香港的細節。」<br />\n<br />\n國安法襲港，外國紛紛打開大門招手，不少港人心灰意冷，熱議移民各地。過去一年，參與了很多次反修例運動遊行的奈緒子，卻想&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n在香港，沒有意義的存在<br />\n<br />\n初約奈緒子，才見她滿頭大汗地趕來，說著流利國語、夾雜著「唔鹹唔淡」的廣東話，讓人感覺她不那麼「日本」。<br />\n大學時期修讀藝術的她，畢業後&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n2014 年雨傘運動，奈緒子在 Facebook 上傳了在夏慤道拍攝的連儂牆相片。人生第一次參與社會運動，看到香港人站在同一路上，為自己發聲，她自言很感觸，皆因在她曾身處的日本社會，很多人面對政府的腐敗、不公義的情況，都不會站出來反對和提出意見，「（日本人）都是覺得安安靜靜比較好。」<br />\n<br />\n不要逃避 因為這是我的家<br />\n<br />\n國安法襲港，各國的移民大門漸開，不少港人都考慮離開香港。作為一個移居香港的日本人，奈緒子卻沒有移民的想法&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"890be115c42a21c7446147ac9ab3166846895150","tid":2159399,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T10:35:28.000Z","msg":"多謝您"},{"pid":"702c90fc8eae856e12a1db918d183bb0e279c383","tid":2159399,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T15:51:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e3234448bde042de59a6b3d174457281812489f","tid":2159399,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"702c90fc8eae856e12a1db918d183bb0e279c383","tid":2159399,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T15:51:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T17:59:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我香港wo，有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}